data.description: Move in ready! Step into this beautifully updated South Fulton home with contemporary upgrades, including a new furnace, roof, and elegant light fixtures. The main level boasts a formal living room, dining area, and a spacious kitchen connected to a family room with a practical half-bath. Upstairs, the oversized primary suite features a fireplace, sitting area, three closets, and a large bathroom. Generously sized secondary bedrooms and another bathroom complete this home, seamlessly blending tradition with modern convenience for a space that creates lasting memories.
